nd-color:#09090b !important;padding:16px 32px 40px;border-top:1px solid #1c1c1f;"><p style="color:#3f3f46 !important;font-size:11px;margin:0;">Complerer · Compliance Platform</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>',
